{"data":[{"date":"07:29 18/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hai \u0111\u1ed9i?</h2><br>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: M\u1ed9t tr\u1eddi m\u1ed9t v\u1ef1c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\" target=\"_blank\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i </span>t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh th\u00eam c\u1ea3 V-League 2017 v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u00fap QG 2018 th\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i n\u00ean con s\u1ed1 20.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n sau 13 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Thanh H\u00f3a hay HAGL. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u1ebb kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Moses gi\u00e0u c\u01a1 b\u1eafp khu trung tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Oseni \u0111ang l\u00e0 hung th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 V-League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Sau-vong-14-V-League-2018-Ha-Noi,-HAGL-dong-loat-nga-ngua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-1 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u00edt ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi 7 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 13.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd ghi 15 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec gi\u1ea3i, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean con s\u1ed1 24 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u1ea1i theo m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eady m\u00e0 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m l\u00e0 Da Sylva l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 &lsquo;v\u01b0\u01a1n vai&rsquo; \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League 2018, m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay 12 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u01a1 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ea1ch?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi xa l\u1ea1 vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n hay SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 &lsquo;anh em m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0&rsquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ed7 Quang Hi\u1ec3n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1eddi \u0111\u00f4 v\u00e0o Nam c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby v\u00e0 t\u1eebng n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n Giang \u0110\u00f4ng, c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0 b\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y r\u00e0ng bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i V-League. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 &lsquo;ru\u1ed9t th\u1ecbt&rsquo; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e9p d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn 100% tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u trung th\u1ef1c, cao th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi thua dam Sai Gon o vong 14 V-League 2018.\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ea1ch \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, Bongda24h xin kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 n\u00eau ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c quan t\u00e2m sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra chuy\u1ec7n cho \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i V-League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a</span><br>\r\nV\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu thua \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. N\u00f3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nHLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3678","checkdouble":"188784"},{"date":"21:16 17/06","title":"HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eefng t\u1eadt x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, HAGL \u0111ang c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong ba v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai thua Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (0-3), Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (2-3) v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (1-2) d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Minh Phuong that vong vi HAGL bat dau da tieu xao.\" title=\"HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn HAGL r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9 trong BXH V-League 2018. Ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed1i lo v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn 8 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau ba tr\u1eadn, HAGL c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i x\u1ea5u sau v\u00e0i n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf V-League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HAGL ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn 5 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i kh\u00e1c nhau, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Kim Jinseo. T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea1p Ewonder (\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL d\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc: &quot;Th\u1eadt bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfc cho l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a HAGL, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t d\u1ea7n l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eebng l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc. H\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, c\u00e3i tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u00edt th\u1ea5y \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1ch h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 HAGL c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea1p khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 c\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ednh th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o. T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u00e1n k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c sau pha b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1p ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Duy M\u1ea1nh (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i). Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1p Rosa Tardin Douglas (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3677","checkdouble":"188742"},{"date":"21:19 17/06","title":"\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV SLNA d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen vi\u1ec7n binh t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/danh-bai-binh-duong-hlv-slna-het-loi-khen-vien-binh-tu-flc-thanh-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/6, CLB SLNA b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 sau hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a H\u1ed3 Tu\u1ea5n T\u00e0i v\u00e0 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u2018l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\u2019 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV SLNA khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV SLNA khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/danh-bai-binh-duong-hlv-slna-het-loi-khen-vien-binh-tu-flc-thanh-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 11 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 14 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cSau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a SLNA \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mang ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p CLB B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng SLNA l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00ec t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean 3 b\u00e0n. May m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi SLNA v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng SLNA c\u0169ng gi\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Vinh theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cV\u0103n B\u00ecnh v\u1eeba m\u1edbi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, n\u00ean th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi V\u0103n B\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi gian quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ec3 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng\u201d, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i nh\u01b0ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Ngh\u1ec7 An. V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i binh t\u1ed1t th\u00ec SLNA c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfn xa tr\u00ean BXH V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3676","checkdouble":"188744"},{"date":"23:56 17/06","title":"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-tran-hoa-cua-argentina-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm l\u00e0 do CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m gi\u1ed1ng Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 \u1edf 13 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean V-League 2018 nh\u01b0ng khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-5. Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, trong khi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u1ed1p cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Van Tai Em tiet lo ly do Ha Noi thua dam.\" title=\"HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/tai-em.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Oseni nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Sau \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00fa poker c\u1ee7a Da Sylva, trong khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng nh\u1edd World Cup 2018<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Iceland vs Argentina. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc theo tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iceland, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap h\u1ecd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina vs Iceland t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018&quot; - HLV T\u00e0i Em ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: &quot;Ngay c\u1ea3 Iceland c\u0169ng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 Argentina, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Iceland v\u1eeba qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean anh em c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee9 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp tinh th\u1ea7n Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. N\u1ebfu Da Sylva c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u00ec S\u00e0i G\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0 CLB TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3675","checkdouble":"188752"},{"date":"00:25 18/06","title":"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Trong 13 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn 5 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi thua dam Sai Gon o vong 14 V-League 2018.\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em cho bi\u1ebft b\u00ed quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc theo tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iceland t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Iceland \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 quan, th\u00eam n\u1eefa l\u00e0 &quot;ph\u00e1 s\u1ee9c&quot; theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khuya t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i: &quot;H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi kh\u00e1t khao kh\u00f4ng cao, c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi World Cup \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 thua nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-2 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00f2n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd pressing ngay \u1edf ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018, b\u1ecb Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3674","checkdouble":"188754"},{"date":"06:01 18/06","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu thua \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y V-League lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n\r\n</h2><br />\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua s\u1ed1c S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Oseni. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3 \u2018h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Sau-vong-14-V-League-2018-Ha-Noi,-HAGL-dong-loat-nga-ngua-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u1ebft b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n, ngo\u1ea1i binh Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 5-2 chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi an to\u00e0n khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft v\u1eabn \u0111ang gi\u1eef c\u1ef1 ly an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HAGL nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 9 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ai ng\u1edd trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 HAGL s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n chi\u1ec1u 17/6 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa cho th\u1ea5y HAGL v\u1eabn c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/dsc_0341-2030.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ea2nh: Bongda.com.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa m\u1ecfng c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecf ph\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u2018h\u1ed3i chu\u00f4ng c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh\u2019 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HAGL kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean BXH nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Highlight-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 SLNA v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o TP.HCM xu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. Thua 0-2 chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, TP.HCM ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn play-off ho\u1eb7c x\u1ea5u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League 2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf V-League n\u0103m nay th\u00ec cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh cho nh\u1eefng su\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, c\u1ea3 SLNA, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec1u \u2018\u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n\u2019 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh su\u1ea5t r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\nXem th\u00eam: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/ket-qua-25.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, LT\u0110, BXH V-League 2018</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o</span><br />\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eefng t\u1eadt x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\">HLV HAGL th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn thua SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nHLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3673","checkdouble":"188775"},{"date":"14:23 17/06","title":"Taxi m\u1ea5t l\u00e1i \u0111\u00e2m v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m C\u0110V Mexico \u0111\u1ebfn Nga xem World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/taxi-mat-lai-dam-vao-nhom-cdv-mexico-den-nga-xem-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc taxi m\u1ea5t l\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e2m th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111ang \u0111i b\u1ed9 tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1 Moscow khi\u1ebfn 8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1ee5 tai n\u1ea1n v\u1eeba x\u1ea3y ra h\u00f4m qua khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kinh s\u1ee3. Ngay t\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1 Moscow, 1 chi\u1ebfc taxi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e2m th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111ang \u0111i b\u1ed9.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/russia-taxi-crash-1384064.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, c\u00f3 8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Moscow xem World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 qu\u00e1n Mexico sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Nga kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tai n\u1ea1n ngo\u00e0i \u00fd mu\u1ed1n cho d\u00f9 video h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho th\u1ea5y l\u00e1i xe taxi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u00fd lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng. Sau khi g\u00e2y tai n\u1ea1n, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf ch\u1ea1y nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111u\u1ed5i theo v\u00e0 b\u1eaft l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf n\u00e0y mang b\u1eb1ng l\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Kyrgyzstan. Danh t\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 Anarbek uulu Chyngiz. Chyngiz khai r\u1eb1ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00eda c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t t\u00e1i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ee5 tai n\u1ea1n \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 \u201ckh\u1ee7ng b\u1ed1\u201d. L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Nga v\u1eabn \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ebft c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n cho World Cup n\u0103m nay.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3672","checkdouble":"188717"},{"date":"13:43 17/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 0-1 HAGL (H1): Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t ghi b\u00e0n si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-vs-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/da-nang-vs-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188715.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u00c0 N\u1eb4NG VS HAGL</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3671","checkdouble":"188715"},{"date":"17:56 17/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-da-nang-vs-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, clip highlights tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL: 0-1<br />\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (8')<br />\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/171152-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-09.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a HAGL v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n HAGL&nbsp;c\u0169ng rung chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u00fat ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 25m so v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i cu\u1ed9n v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n H\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n mi\u1ebfng, tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n HAGL nh\u01b0ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd h\u01a1n, HAGL c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 1-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3670","checkdouble":"188724"},{"date":"16:01 17/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP S\u00c0I G\u00d2N VS H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3669","checkdouble":"188725"},{"date":"16:53 17/06","title":"Sergio Ramos khi\u1ebfn Conte kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/19/sergio-ramos-khien-conte-khong-the-dan-dat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sergio Ramos ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Antonio Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Los Blancos.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real nh\u1eafm Conte thay Zidane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi HLV Zidane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay Real Madrid, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 Wenger, Pochettino v\u00e0 Joachim Low.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Antonio Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergio Ramos ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Antonio Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/sergio-ramos-khien-conte-khong-the-dan-dat-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n kh\u00e1c. Theo Don Balon, Los Blancos nh\u1eafm HLV Antonio Conte c\u1ee7a Chelsea thay th\u1ebf Zidane.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nConte v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. Real Madrid tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Conte v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, \u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 Real \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ramos ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Conte t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-188046.html\" target=\"_blank\">Conte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real</span>, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Los Blancos. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Chelsea s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian thay v\u00ec d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Sergio Ramos\" title=\"trung ve Sergio Ramos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/Sergio-Ramos-muon-Real-Madrid-mua-Milan-Skriniar-cua-Inter-Milan--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sergio Ramos kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1edd Sport c\u1ee7a TBN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Sergio Ramos ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Antonio Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Ramos \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Conte, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Julen Lopetegui.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Chelsea, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Conte. Ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eeb Cesar Azpilicueta th\u00ec nh\u1eefng\u00a0Marcos Alonso, Cesc Fabregas, Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 Pedro \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Diego Costa c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t tin nh\u1eafn. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Real Madrid c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN, Ramos s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng Conte s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ea1i Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3668","checkdouble":"188726"},{"date":"15:04 17/06","title":"\"Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Milinkovic-Savic\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/25/ngoai-hang-anh-la-ben-do-hoan-hao-voi-milinkovicsavic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hernan Crespo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina tin ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU v\u00e0 Man City theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Serie A 2017/18.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hernan Crespo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hernan Crespo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Hernan-Crespo-phat-bieu-ve-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ghi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-milinkovicsavic-len-100-trieu-bang-172-186876.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Ngo\u00e0i hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh, PSG, Real v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cPogba c\u1ee7a Serbia\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hernan Crespo khuy\u00ean Milinkovic-Savic t\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hernan Crespo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina tin ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/16/Igli-Tare-phat-bieu-ve-Milinkovic-Savic-va-su-that-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hernan Crespo khuy\u00ean\u00a0</span>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic t\u1edbi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Milinkovic-Savic s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ebfn Anh Milinkovic-Savic s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Milinkovic-Savic, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Lazio s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Milinkovic-Savic \u1edf l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3667","checkdouble":"188720"},{"date":"16:53 17/06","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/mu-chot-57-trieu-bang-cho-hau-ve-cua-inter-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Milan Skriniar c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Milan Skriniar c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Milan Skriniar c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/18/MU-muon-mua-Milan-Skriniar-cua-Inter-Milan-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Alderweireld\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Smalling v\u00e0 Lindelof ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f2n Jones v\u00e0 Rojo th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng bu\u1ed9c Mourinho ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a M.U nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, anh c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Tottenham, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 thi\u1ec7n ch\u00ed trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Spurs \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel Levy kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alderweireld.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ESPN v\u00e0 Daily Mail \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0a tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-vu-sao-khung-tottenham-172-188260.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Alderweireld</span>, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda\u00a0Tottenham. Mourinho s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU chi 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Inter Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gazzetta dello Sport\u00a0 \u0111\u01b0a tin, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Milan Skriniar c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Milan Skriniar c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Milan Skriniar c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mu-chot-57-trieu-bang-cho-hau-ve-cua-inter-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Milan Skriniar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Milan Skriniar n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sampdoria c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Inter Milan anh c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Skriniar ra s\u00e2n trong 38 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Inter \u1edf Serie A, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMilan Skriniar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.\u00a0 Anh c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Old Trafford, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi t\u1edbi 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Inter Milan b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Slovakia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3666","checkdouble":"188723"}]}